Cloning the forked repo: instructions from https://help.github.com/articles/fork-a-repo/

#git clone https://github.com/totosolat/TauLabs.git

#cd TauLabs/

check your upstream:
#git remote -v

change upstream
#git remote add upstream https://github.com/TauLabs/TauLabs.git

check your upstream again, should be "https://github.com/TauLabs/TauLabs.git"
#git remote -v

--------------------------------------------
sync with the upstream: instructions from https://help.github.com/articles/syncing-a-fork/

#git fetch upstream

#git checkout next

#git merge upstream/next


